# Complete Claude Skills Overview

## Currently Available Skills in This Conversation

Here are all the specialized skills I have access to right now:

### Document & Presentation Skills

- **docx** - Create, edit, and analyze Word documents with tracked changes, comments, and formatting
- **pdf** - Extract text/tables, create PDFs, merge/split documents, and handle PDF forms
- **pptx** - Create and edit PowerPoint presentations with layouts and speaker notes
- **xlsx** - Create and work with Excel spreadsheets including formulas, formatting, and data analysis

### Productivity & Integration Skills

- **recent-emails** - List recent Gmail emails (sent, received, drafted, or starred)
- **recent-files** - Discover recently modified Google Drive files with metadata
- **search-calendar** - Search Google Calendar with natural language queries
- **work-day** - Manage SNMG18 Working Docs directory structure by date
- **work-day-files** - List files in work-day folders with summaries
- **reverse-date** - Convert dates to ISO format (YYYY-MM-DD)
- **reverse-month** - Convert dates to year-month format (YYYY-MM)
- **news-snapshot** - Get current news summaries with sources

### Specialized Creation Skills

- **new-product** - Generate enterprise AI product white papers from Google Drive documentation
- **new-presentation** - Create presentations using Steve Jobs's 3-Second Rule methodology
- **presentation-outline** - Transform Google Docs into structured presentation outlines
- **sentient-brand-guidelines** - Apply Sentient.io branding to marketing materials

### Development & Reference Skills

- **skill-creator** - Guide for creating new custom skills
- **product-self-knowledge** - Authoritative information about Anthropic products
- **brand-guidelines** - Apply Anthropic's brand colors and typography (example skill)
- **algorithmic-art** - Create generative art using p5.js (example skill)

